name: OralContraceptivePillsRXNORMMedications
title: Oral Contraceptive Pills RXNORM Medications
description: For Contraceptive eCQMs Approval for Trial Use application in Spring 2022; This set contains medication codes for oral contraceptive pills.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Family planning - provision and use of most and moderately effective contraceptive methods),(Data Element Scope: Medication codes for oral contraceptive pill, a moderately effective method of contraception),(Inclusion Criteria: Medication codes for oral contraceptive pill, a moderately effective method of contraception),(Exclusion Criteria: Any contraceptive method that is not an oral contraceptive pill; Most effective (i.e., sterilization, IUDs/IUSs, contraceptive implants) or moderately effective (i.e., injectables, patch, or ring) methods of contraception; Less effective methods of contraception (i.e., diaphragm, male condom, female condom, withdrawal, sponge, fertility-awareness based methods, spermicide); excludes oral pills for emergency contraception and hormone replacement therapy)
